be.docarch.odt2braille.addon
Class SettingsDialog

java.lang.Object
  be.docarch.odt2braille.addon.SettingsDialog

public class SettingsDialog
extends java.lang.Object

Show an OpenOffice.org dialog window for adjusting the braille settings. The dialog has 3 tabs:

  • General Settings
  • Languages Settings (only enabled if the document contains multiple languages)
  • Emboss/Export Settings

Author:
Bert Frees
